### Will be empty at first

GET http://localhost:8080/greetings HTTP/1.1

### This is the same post-URL rewriting

GET http://localhost:8080/api/Greetings HTTP/1.1


### Now add a Greetings

POST http://localhost:8080/greetings HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "Message" : "Hello World"
}

### Now see that greeting

GET http://localhost:8080/greetings/{ec687094-dc8d-4f85-9c35-269cbe7c5ee2} HTTP/1.1


### Now add some more greetings

POST http://localhost:8080/greetings HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "Message" : "Hello Mary"
}

### And even more

POST http://localhost:8080/greetings HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "Message" : "Hello Alice"
}


### Now see all the greeetings

GET http://localhost:8080/greetings HTTP/1.1

